  "texts": [
    "This time, however, Jonah's message was met with a different response.",
    "The king himself heard of Jonah's decree and took immediate action.",
    "He ordered a city-wide fast and urged his people to repent from their wicked ways.",
    "Jonah was astonished by the king's humility and sincerity.",
    "This was not the response he had expected from a people whose hearts were hardened towards God."
